Magarpatta (Marathi: मगरपट्टा lit. Land of Magars) is a privately owned Gated community in Hadapsar area of Pune, India. Magarpatta is built over 600 acres of land. It is home to a commercial zone, residential neighbourhoods, a multi specialty hospital, a shopping mall, multiple restaurants, a gymkhana and a large 25 acre park called Aditi Garden. It has eco-friendly development and has green spaces that make up for 30 per cent of the area. Additionally, it is home to two schools: Magarpatta City Public School and Vibgyor School.
Magarpatta City comes under pincode 411028.
